{"remainingRequest":"/Users/baidu/work/git/mywork/lixiaoqing1208.github.io/node_modules/vue-loader/lib/index.js??ref--1-1!/Users/baidu/work/git/mywork/lixiaoqing1208.github.io/node_modules/vuepress/lib/webpack/markdownLoader.js??ref--1-2!/Users/baidu/work/git/mywork/lixiaoqing1208.github.io/adaptation/accessibility/robust/different-resolution.md?vue&type=template&id=2efdacce&","dependencies":[{"path":"/Users/baidu/work/git/mywork/lixiaoqing1208.github.io/adaptation/accessibility/robust/different-resolution.md","mtime":1540958169773},{"path":"/Users/baidu/work/git/mywork/lixiaoqing1208.github.io/node_modules/cache-loader/dist/cjs.js","mtime":499162500000},{"path":"/Users/baidu/work/git/mywork/lixiaoqing1208.github.io/node_modules/vue-loader/lib/loaders/templateLoader.js","mtime":499162500000},{"path":"/Users/baidu/work/git/mywork/lixiaoqing1208.github.io/node_modules/cache-loader/dist/cjs.js","mtime":499162500000},{"path":"/Users/baidu/work/git/mywork/lixiaoqing1208.github.io/node_modules/vue-loader/lib/index.js","mtime":499162500000},{"path":"/Users/baidu/work/git/mywork/lixiaoqing1208.github.io/node_modules/vuepress/lib/webpack/markdownLoader.js","mtime":1533872387000}],"contextDependencies":[],"result":["\n<div class=\"content\"><h1 id=\"不同分辨率适配\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#不同分辨率适配\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a> 不同分辨率适配</h1>\n<h2 id=\"描述\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#描述\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a> 描述</h2>\n<p>当前的移动杂屏时代，存在很多设备具有不同分辨率的情况，如果采用固定的布局就会出现页面非常大或者非常小，页面不能完整呈现或者页面空白太多等问题，导致用户体验很差。因此需要完善的适配方案来保证用户在不同分辨率的情况下都能有完美的呈现。</p>\n<h2 id=\"例子\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#例子\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a> 例子</h2>\n<h3 id=\"good-case\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#good-case\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a> good case</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>lavas 官网在pc上面的展现，导航横向显示</p>\n  <img src=\"https://agroup-bos.su.bcebos.com/1354f3b1580af07accad397c0e018c294e8ff3b1\" alt=\"lavas\" width=\"250\">\n<p>在移动上面也能完美适配，将过多的导航收起放在右侧隐藏起来</p>\n  <img src=\"https://agroup-bos.su.bcebos.com/16519e0e5325791afe8df62ba5e98fa44cbae677\" alt=\"lavas\" width=\"250\">\n<p>当点击右侧按钮之后导航才纵向显示出来，合理的利用了空间</p>\n  <img src=\"https://agroup-bos.su.bcebos.com/256feb5d2fbb3063b642180303a9279e6a2bf16e\" alt=\"lavas\" width=\"250\">\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"指导建议\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#指导建议\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a> 指导建议</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>使用rem等单位来相对缩放</li>\n<li>使用media query根据不同设备做适配</li>\n<li>定义viewport宽度</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"相关文档\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#相关文档\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a> 相关文档</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/riskers/blog/issues/17\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">移动端适配方案(上)<OutboundLink/></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/riskers/blog/issues/18\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">移动端适配方案(下)<OutboundLink/></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n",null]}